# e625f477997a4e68a2b8251ef64d9a49
msgid "A screenshot of Control Panel started from the KDE desktop can be seen in Figure 8.a."
msgstr ""

#: ../../controlpanel.rst:15
# 21f54caefcae40aab88ada26a896a8c7
msgid "**Figure 8.a: PC-BSD® Control Panel**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../controlpanel.rst:19
# a54a99678d6c44f59fead4323b1e79be
msgid "The available utilities are divided into sections. If you click a grey section bar, you can toggle between displaying (bar has up arrow) or hiding (bar has down arrow) its icons. In this example, the display for the \"Desktop environment\" section is hidden."
