#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1155
# 02c317e8803849deb37a3216d96e93bf
msgid "Press \"OK\" in the pop-up menu. This will prompt you to input and confirm the password to associate with the device. Another message will ask if you are ready. Click \"Yes\" to initialize the device. The User Manager screen will be greyed out while the device is prepared. Once the initialization is complete, the User Manager screen will change to display the device's key options, as seen in Figure 8.9e."
