# 4b41302b5d0f468a88c659f628820ec4
msgid "To add or delete custom firewall rules, click the \"Open Ports\" tab to open the screen shown in Figure 8.17b. Note that your custom rules will allow **incoming** connections on the specified protocol and port number."
